708366f-a.text:
154-158 Fifth Ave., at the N.W. corner of West 20th Street, showing Wm. Knabe and Company, Piano Manufacturers occupying the corner store in the Presbyterian Building. Buildings shown on the left, adjoining the corner are No. 5 and Westward. No. 11 is the 9-story structure and is newly constructed.

Prior to 1903.

George Barlow Collection.
Gift of George D. Chinn.
